# Demo editor logins for `next dev` ONLY; set real values (and a real
# secret) in your host's environment for production, with passwordHash
# entries from `npx editsy hash-password`. Add EDITSY_SMTP_URL to enable
# "email me a login link".
EDITSY_SECRET=dev-only-secret-do-not-use-in-production
